latestPosts.caption:
GOOD VIBES ONLY. 💗

At ColourPop, everything we do and every decision we make begins with YOU! To make sure we never forget, we put U at the center of our brand: Colo-U-rPop.

We’re dedicated to celebrating creators from all backgrounds and communities. To maintain an environment that is inclusive, safe, and uplifting for all, we do not tolerate any hate or negativity directed at those we feature on our page.

Your feedback is important to us, and we are always here to listen and engage. By providing your feedback thoughtfully and respectfully, we empower each other to continually improve and excel, creating a supportive environment where everyone can grow and thrive. 🌱

To ensure that our platform remains an inclusive, safe, respectful and supportive space for all, we reserve the right to delete any comments that promote hate or negativity - especially when directed toward others. Please help us keep our page a safe space for all by keeping the comment section thoughtful and kind.

Xoxo, Your ColourPop Fam 💕
